# 18_06 Person with FOAF/schema multiple expressions per label

person [Sarah Chen
  - name | foaf:name | schema:name [Sarah Chen]
  - email | foaf:mbox | schema:email [sarah@example.edu]
  - works for | foaf:workplaceHomepage | schema:worksFor [
    - name | schema:name [University Research Center]
    - url | schema:url [<https://university.edu>]
  ]
]
